<p>Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky said he will travel to Washington this week and expects to meet President Trump on Friday to focus on bolstering Ukraine’s air defenses, potential long-range weapons, and increasing pressure on Russia [ndtv.com#1][japantoday.com#1][theglobeandmail.com#1]. The White House meeting is planned for Friday, following a recent call in which the leaders discussed the possibility of Ukraine acquiring Tomahawk missiles [politico.com#1]. President Trump has said he may send Tomahawk missiles to Ukraine, while Zelensky is seeking U.S. consideration of long-range capabilities [bbc.com#1][theglobeandmail.com#1]. Zelensky also plans to meet U.S. defense and energy companies and members of Congress during the visit, and has linked optimism for Ukraine to Trump’s recent Gaza ceasefire negotiations [theglobeandmail.com#1][theguardian.com#1][politico.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/yJ3garaW2WwbhDqmz2zCA1hb2CCuOkaaZJiW_8k168L1pizJrWQPdgfTPv998k0r6u3qyoE0hWga9VUpCsbBfwuN9sMkJF4rLox8VcbBvi9KTcDeqqDTnPECkBhCiPMsudrmGQ0pT_rtgBSFoSlUNRSnYrpNOnYMmwMotE2iKQyxbR7xhl6A023Cyi5ZGmmLu2o-x8LQW_tGfRL25b8nlP8rbISXHU7sx4KknbYmUw4-m5ROtQWGmXZfsSlRnEo1vxSEqbSE4DO0XgxA7g' alt='Ukraine’s president Volodymyr Zelensky plans Washington talks and meetings with U.S. companies and lawmakers.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Friday meeting: A White House meeting between President Trump and President Zelensky is planned for Friday in Washington [politico.com#1][ndtv.com#1][japantoday.com#1].</li><li>Air defense focus: Zelensky said the agenda includes strengthening Ukraine’s air defenses and increasing pressure on Russia [ndtv.com#1][japantoday.com#1].</li><li>Long-range options: Trump says he may send Tomahawk missiles, and the leaders discussed Kyiv potentially acquiring them in a recent call [bbc.com#1][politico.com#1].</li><li>Broader outreach: During the trip, Zelensky will meet U.S. defense and energy companies and members of Congress [theglobeand